## Execution Patterns

### Tag-Based Execution
```bash
# Run BizomWebAPI suite
mvn test -Dcucumber.filter.tags="@BizomWebAPI"

# Run IntegrationAPI suite
mvn test -Dcucumber.filter.tags="@Execution"

# Run specific module within IntegrationAPI
mvn test -Dcucumber.filter.tags="@Execution and @Orders"

# Run positive scenarios
mvn test -Dcucumber.filter.tags="@PositiveScenario"

# Run GET requests only
mvn test -Dcucumber.filter.tags="@allGet"
```

### Parallel Execution
```xml
<!-- TestNG XML Configuration for BizomWebAPI -->
<suite name="BizomWebAPI Test Suite" parallel="methods" thread-count="3">
    <test name="BizomWebAPI Tests">
        <classes>
            <class name="com.Bizom.runner.BizomWebAPI_Runner"/>
        </classes>
    </test>
</suite>

<!-- TestNG XML Configuration for IntegrationAPI -->
<suite name="IntegrationAPI Test Suite" parallel="methods" thread-count="3">
    <test name="IntegrationAPI Tests">
        <classes>
            <class name="com.Bizom.runner.IntegrationAPI_Runner"/>
        </classes>
    </test>
</suite>

<!-- TestNG XML Configuration for RetailerAPI -->
<suite name="RetailerAPI Test Suite" parallel="methods" thread-count="3">
    <test name="RetailerAPI Tests">
        <classes>
            <class name="com.Bizom.runner.RetailerAPI_Runner"/>
        </classes>
    </test>
</suite>
```

## Report Generation

### Maven Goals
```bash
# Clean and compile
mvn clean compile

# Run tests and generate reports
mvn test

# Generate Cucumber HTML reports
mvn verify

# Generate Allure reports
allure serve target/allure-results
```

### Report Outputs
- **ExtentReports**: `Execution_Reports/API_Reports/`
- **Cucumber HTML**: `target/cucumber-report-html/`
- **Allure Reports**: `target/allure-results/`
- **JSON Reports**: `target/cucumber.json`

