## CI/CD Integration

### Maven Surefire Plugin
```xml
<plugin>
    <groupId>org.apache.maven.plugins</groupId>
    <artifactId>maven-surefire-plugin</artifactId>
    <version>2.19.1</version>
    <configuration>
        <testFailureIgnore>true</testFailureIgnore>
        <suiteXmlFiles>
            <!-- Choose appropriate TestNG XML based on executionBase -->
            <suiteXmlFile>src/test/resources/NG_XMLs/BizomWebAPI_Testng.xml</suiteXmlFile>
            <!-- OR -->
            <suiteXmlFile>src/test/resources/NG_XMLs/IntegrationAPI_Testng.xml</suiteXmlFile>
            <!-- OR -->
            <suiteXmlFile>src/test/resources/NG_XMLs/RetailerAPI_Testng.xml</suiteXmlFile>
        </suiteXmlFiles>
    </configuration>
</plugin>
```

